quran[15{c,v,t}:
15,1,a l- ray yeh ayaat hain kitaab Ellahi aur quran Mubin kihalal hi behtar aur paindah tar hai
15,2,baeed nahi ke aik waqt woh aa jaye jab wohi log jinhon ne aaj ( dawat islam ko qubool karne se ) inkaar kar diya hai pachta pachta kar kahin ge ke kash hum ne sir tasleem khham kar diya hota
15,3,"chhorro inhain khayen, pi-yen , mazay karen, aur behlawaymein daaley rakhay inn ko jhooti umeed anqareeb aِnhin maloom ho jaye ga"
15,4,hum ne iss se pehlay jis bastii ko bhi halaak kya hai is ke liye aik khaas mohlat amal likhi ja chuki thi
15,5,"koi qoum nah apne waqt muqarrar se pehlay halaak hosakti hai, nah uss ke baad chhuut sakti hai"
15,6,"yeh log kehte hain"" ae woh shakhs jis par zikar nazil howa hai, to yaqeenan deewana hai"
15,7,"agar to sacha hai to hamaray samnay firshton ko le kyun nahi aata? """
15,8,"hum firshton ko yun hi nahi utaar diya karte woh jab utartay hain to haq ke sath utartay hain, aur phir logon ko mohlat nahi di jati"
15,9,"raha yeh zikar, to iss ko hum ne nazil kya hai aur hum khud iss ke nigehbaan hain"
15,10,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, hum tum se pehlay bohat si guzri hui qomon mein rasool bhaij chuke hain"
15,11,kabhi aisa nahi howa ke unn ke paas koi rasool aaya ho aur onhon ne uss ka mazaq nah uraya ho
15,12,mujrimeen ke dilon mein to hum is zikar ko isi terhan ( salakh ke manind ) guzartay hain
15,13,woh iss par imaan nahi laya karte qadeem se iss qamash ke logon ka yahi tareeqa chala aa raha hai
15,14,agar hum unn par aasman ka koi darwaaza khol dete aur woh din d_harhe uss mein charhne bhi lagtay
15,15,"tab bhi woh yahi kehte ke hamari aankhon ko dhoka ho raha hai, balkay hum par jaadoo kar diya gaya hai"
